3973b3494: Sun Jun 22 23:19:06 2025 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Added functionality to disable logins

 - You can use the management page to disable logins
 - Logins are not deleted and will not prevent users from logging in.
 - As soon as a disabled user logs in again, the user is enabled again
 - Disabled users are not visible when sharing projects

Also modified the management page so thatit is easier to handle installations with
many users. You can search users with the selection box

