ef241fee7: Tue Dec 17 16:32:08 2024 +0000 FayCross
New feature that allows enhanced progress bar to be shown in header bar.
This can include progress markers based on pages, chapters or milestones.
New milestone optional property available on all pages that allows you to mark up milestone pages for use as progress markers.
Milestone pages will be shown with a special icon in the editor.

