523424507: Mon Dec 16 14:13:52 2024 +0000 Ron Mitchell
first draft of hide/show code added to relevant content types. This works but arguably has a lot of repetition.
Also two current issues:
1. stripping out the word 'page' from the hidden alert so that it just says "this is hidden" rather than "this page is hidden" probably isn't the right way to do this.
The hide code isn't yet added to the contents of navigators so although the hide/show options show for contents added to navigators in the wizard at the moment this will not doing anything. But hiding the whole navigator does work.

