be87321ac: Wed Oct 24 21:54:52 2018 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Facilitate branding og workspace

=======================================================

aed0f1df8: Wed Oct 24 20:30:00 2018 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Only prevent restarting exercises when tracking first pass

