0353024e7: Sun Feb 12 16:55:25 2017 +0000 Smith, John
Fix #563 - A better way to solve this. We sort the glossary terms by longest and only alphabetise sort alphabetically for display in Glossary page model. Subset phrases are always shorter so always checked after the longer phrase has been linked.

