0c1b4d6b6: Fri Feb 10 15:58:45 2017 +0000 Smith, John
Fix for #563 - reverse the order that we check for glossary terms. For terms such as ‘due’ and ‘due date’, the shorter always appears first (alphabetical) but the latter should be replaced first (as it is the best match).

