=======================================================

2419f1333: Sun Jul 3 21:10:57 2016 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Fix several problems with the SCORM tracking

 - SCORM 1.2 player of Moodle doesn't except scores and weights with more than
   two decimals. This caused always a zero score if the result was not 100%
 - SCORM 1.2 matching result was encoded wrong
 - SCORM resulted in failed object if all the interactions have a weight
   of 0.0

