9413b3b6e: Tue Apr 5 18:33:00 2016 -0300 LeoRodz
Fix issues with suspend_data and score

The suspend_data was not saved when course becomes "completed" so the last visited page was not recorded as visited.
With a SCORM First Pass Tracking Mode course the first score was not preserved if we revisit any page that report a score.
=======================================================

