- Chart: Added 'Summary' to xwd to provide alt for canvas
- Chart & table: improved appearance when text is responsive
- Interactive List: fixed bug where links showing as 'visited' when weren't
- Stimulating Q & Button Sequence: aria-live used to read new info when revealed
- Model Answer & MA Results: Fixed bug where line breaks were being lost in info from previous pages

=======================================================

8f96c8b62: Thu Mar 10 11:04:32 2016 +0000 FayCross
Continued accessibility improvements to media pages

=======================================================

d2610412b: Wed Mar 9 15:46:27 2016 +0000 FayCross
Accessibility improvements to media pages:
- Removed unnecessary tabindexes
- Changed order of some elements so screen reader reading order is more logical
- Added hidden screen reader instructions where needed
- Used aria-label to add more meaningful link descriptions and warn when links will open in new window
- Image viewer now shows highlight around image when focused and using arrow keys to move around it
- Added icon to transcript buttons
- Fixed bug where audio player controls weren't reading out button labels to Jaws screen reader
- Fixed bug where video control bar sometimes wasn't accessible when only using keyboard
- Changed the occasional bit of text that wasn't being responsive

