=======================================================

bf3292918: Fri Mar 4 09:46:00 2016 +0100 Tom Reijnders
Fixed #422: export not working on default XAMPP installation on OSX

=======================================================

7e26fdeb1: Wed Mar 2 17:08:03 2016 +0000 FayCross
Accessibility improvements to navigator pages:
- Removed unnecessary tabindexes
- Changed order of some elements so screen reader reading order is more logical
- Made keyboard controls more consistent (e.g. can tab to everything - don't have to swap between tab & arrows to access other tabs)
- Added hidden screen reader instructions where needed
- Fixed bug where screen readers couldn't access panel contents on tabNav page
- Used aria-live so changes to page content is announced immediately by screen reader
- Used aria-labelled to add more meaningful link descriptions and warn when links will open in new window
- Used aria-hidden to hide LO & title page background images from screen readers as we don't add alt text for them
- Changed icons used on slideshow page so they're more obvious (now uses Font Awesome icons)

XWD changes:
- Column Page: Added show column titles option(previously what you entered here wasn't used anywhere)
- Hyperlinks: Page text was wrongly titled as page title

