Prevent tags from showing in play/preview window title (firefox)

=======================================================

8e3341281: Sat Jan 30 20:14:19 2016 +0100 Tom Reijnders
Improve compatibillity with IE: force IE compatibillity mode off

1. Make sure all html documents start with this on the FIRST line:

<!DOCTYPE html>

2. Make sure these are the FIRST 3 meta tags in the header:
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">

