bd4c561ed: Thu Jul 16 11:57:31 2015 +0100 FayCross
Changed dragDropLabel model - New optional properties 'Label Position' & 'Image Width'. Improved image size responsiveness.
Changed x_scaleImg function in xenith.js as it was allowing all images to be scaled above their original size.
Changed hotspotImage.html & connectorHotspotImage.html so images can't be scaled above their original size.

=======================================================

a5f399351: Thu Jul 16 11:57:31 2015 +0100 FayCross
Changed dragDropLabel model - New optional properties 'Label Position' & 'Image Width'. Improved image size responsiveness.
Changed x_scaleImg function in xenith.js as it was allowing all images to be scaled above their original size.
Changed hotspotImage.html & connectorHotspotImage.html so images can't be scaled above their original size.

