b609b4eda: Thu Jun 4 15:16:25 2015 +0100 FayCross
Improvements to gap fill page (requested by user at UoN) to allow gaps to have several possible correct answers. Possible answers should be separated by /
e.g. The union jack is |red/white/blue|, |red/white/blue|, and |red/white/blue|.

=======================================================

ad6f81375: Thu Jun 4 15:16:25 2015 +0100 FayCross
Improvements to gap fill page (requested by user at UoN) to allow gaps to have several possible correct answers. Possible answers should be separated by /
e.g. The union jack is |red/white/blue|, |red/white/blue|, and |red/white/blue|.

