9dcfe97ce: Thu May 14 15:14:04 2015 +0100 FayCross
Various changes to page XWDs & models. Including:
- Removed lots of unnecessary properties from nestedPage (now only used in navigators)
- Changed transcriptReader page to use nestedSynch instead of nestedPage
- Deprecated various optional properties only relevant to Flash LO or editor (e.g. text colour, superscript support & button width)
- Standardised capitalisation of labels in wizard
- Removed wysiwyg from fields where it's not relevant
- Changed some label text to make it clearer

This is ongoing, still need to look at Interactivity, Connector & Misc pages

Fixed bug in title page that was stopping bg image loading

=======================================================

a5e528e76: Thu May 14 15:14:04 2015 +0100 FayCross
Various changes to page XWDs & models. Including:
- Removed lots of unnecessary properties from nestedPage (now only used in navigators)
- Changed transcriptReader page to use nestedSynch instead of nestedPage
