0269f9d05: Fri May 1 13:44:53 2015 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Fixed #234 - Editor - Content not saved when changing between pages

- This was caused by an earlier fix to fix non-working font-colour widgets
  of inline editors
- All the ckeditor intances of a page are destroyed before building the
  new page. This caused a race condition with the event handling

=======================================================

e0ee0e3da: Fri May 1 13:44:53 2015 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Fixed #234 - Editor - Content not saved when changing between pages

- This was caused by an earlier fix to fix non-working font-colour widgets
  of inline editors
- All the ckeditor intances of a page are destroyed before building the
  new page. This caused a race condition with the event handling

