887e0896e: Fri Mar 6 14:48:02 2015 +0000 John Smith
Added a few more types in to the fix for #196

Going to re-open this issue because this takes care of some of the textboxes however there are some textareas like "embed code" that also probably need to be handled gracefully. Also, it ignores boxes globally by name - this could have repercussions where there are name clashes to I may need to make this more granular, picking out specific field names within certain pagetypes.
=======================================================

b76256571: Fri Mar 6 14:48:02 2015 +0000 John Smith
Added a few more types in to the fix for #196

Going to re-open this issue because this takes care of some of the textboxes however there are some textareas like "embed code" that also probably need to be handled gracefully. Also, it ignores boxes globally by name - this could have repercussions where there are name clashes to I may need to make this more granular, picking out specific field names within certain pagetypes.
=======================================================

