e968dbb31: Fri Feb 27 20:15:18 2015 +0000 Ron Mitchell
3 example themes for Tom to test with. Nothing special here but suitable for testing. Suggesting directory structure of /themes/templatename/themename/themename.css e.g. /themes/Nottingham/darkgrey/darkgrey.css so that we can perhaps have other themes for other templates in future. Suggesting keeping theme directory in root (like moodle) to make it easy to add new themes

Signed-off-by: Ron Mitchell <ronm123@googlemail.com>

=======================================================

919e7fd21: Fri Feb 27 20:15:18 2015 +0000 Ron Mitchell
3 example themes for Tom to test with. Nothing special here but suitable for testing. Suggesting directory structure of /themes/templatename/themename/themename.css e.g. /themes/Nottingham/darkgrey/darkgrey.css so that we can perhaps have other themes for other templates in future. Suggesting keeping theme directory in root (like moodle) to make it easy to add new themes

Signed-off-by: Ron Mitchell <ronm123@googlemail.com>

