39937d36f: Wed Feb 11 15:48:58 2015 +0000 John Smith
Fix to allow vertical scrolling

When the page has to scroll vertically it throws out the calculation so the inclusion of:

 + $("div#x_pageHolder").scrollTop()

fixes this...
