1831ffd30: Wed Dec 10 11:02:48 2014 +0000 FayCross
Fixed video load bug in multiple perspectives where some browsers struggle to load all thumbnails - default thumbnail for videos is now an image. You can override this with an image you upload (optional property) or use the first frame of video.

Header text added to mediaPlayer.js.

=======================================================

