5017ae181: Sun Nov 16 22:13:20 2014 +0100 Tom Reijnders
Implement the possibillity to deprecate parameters in the XWD files

- (optional) parameters can take the attribute deprecated="Reason to
  deprecate"
- Pages can take the attribute deprecated="Reason to deprecate"
- Can mark attributes as flash engine only by adding attribute
  flashonly="true"
- Optional parameters can have attribute tooltip="Explanation of optional
  parameter"

=======================================================

b8dcdc533: Sun Nov 16 22:13:20 2014 +0100 Tom Reijnders
Implement the possibillity to deprecate parameters in the XWD files

- (optional) parameters can take the attribute deprecated="Reason to
  deprecate"
- Pages can take the attribute deprecated="Reason to deprecate"
- Can mark attributes as flash engine only by adding attribute
  flashonly="true"
- Optional parameters can have attribute tooltip="Explanation of optional
  parameter"

