37d6cf5e5: Fri Oct 3 16:58:43 2014 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Replace kcfinder with elfinder image browser

- KCFinder is GPL, which is incompatible with Apereo
- elFinder is BSD
- elFinder works better on tablets

=======================================================

0b884b1b3: Fri Oct 3 16:58:43 2014 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Replace kcfinder with elfinder image browser

- KCFinder is GPL, which is incompatible with Apereo
- elFinder is BSD
- elFinder works better on tablets

