0303ba071: Fri Sep 19 09:47:13 2014 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Add buttons to the drawing editor

Previously, the only way to leave the editor, was close the window, but
then, if you hadn't saved your work, your drawing would be lost.

Adding a 'Save and Exit'and a 'Cancel' button makes it more intuively.

=======================================================

d9d0a52f1: Fri Sep 19 09:47:13 2014 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Add buttons to the drawing editor

Previously, the only way to leave the editor, was close the window, but
then, if you hadn't saved your work, your drawing would be lost.

Adding a 'Save and Exit'and a 'Cancel' button makes it more intuively.

