19418739b: Wed Jul 2 13:37:56 2014 +0100 John Smith
Hide the header logo in site template as logo doesn't exist - issue #63
For installs where logo has been placed at 'modules/site/parent_templates/site/common/img/logo.png' you can add

<style type="text/css">
  #overview div.logo {
    display: inherit;
  }
</style>

And that will again show the div

=======================================================

6363ce995: Wed Jul 2 13:37:56 2014 +0100 John Smith
Hide the header logo in site template as logo doesn't exist - issue #63
For installs where logo has been placed at 'modules/site/parent_templates/site/common/img/logo.png' you can add

<style type="text/css">
  #overview div.logo {
    display: inherit;
  }
</style>

And that will again show the div

=======================================================

