39cda0a55: Tue Jun 17 23:22:36 2014 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Fix xenith run-time

- Glossary with images (or other taggs) doesn't work because a title was
  added with double-quotes.
- In the end decided to leave title out, it showed as a tooltip through
  the Xerte one
- Changed x_AddLineBreaks to not replace the line breaks if the text field
  starts with a <p>, because it is likely to come from the WYSIWIG editor

=======================================================

a5ed3f303: Tue Jun 17 23:22:36 2014 +0200 Tom Reijnders
Fix xenith run-time

- Glossary with images (or other taggs) doesn't work because a title was
  added with double-quotes.
- In the end decided to leave title out, it showed as a tooltip through
  the Xerte one
- Changed x_AddLineBreaks to not replace the line breaks if the text field
  starts with a <p>, because it is likely to come from the WYSIWIG editor

