- Added ckeditor
- Updated jstree to version 3
- followed pattern of original Flash wizard and made sure things are
  presented in the same order
- Divided options in normal, cdata, optional, advanced and language
  options
- Made parsing of attibute values a bit more robust by converting to
  lowercase first (like in th eFlash version)

