476e352b7: Mon Oct 28 20:13:23 2013 +0100 Tom Reijnders
If .zip to imported doesn't have a preview.xml, an empty preview.xml is
generated.

This prevents the newly imported LO to be edited and/or previewed
properly.

=======================================================

d7d8a8581: Mon Oct 28 20:13:23 2013 +0100 Tom Reijnders
If .zip to imported doesn't have a preview.xml, an empty preview.xml is
generated.

This prevents the newly imported LO to be edited and/or previewed
properly.

