3c9c380e0: Thu Jul 25 13:12:45 2013 +0000 John Smith
Moved some code around... and changed last new Object declaration to {}

git-svn-id: https://xerteonlinetoolkits.googlecode.com/svn/trunk@1061 912cdd6b-5c7d-d5a7-a2ba-d0f0cdb91641

=======================================================

75f6a77a8: Wed Jul 24 09:07:55 2013 +0000 John Smith
OPTIMISATION: Changed a few things to make xenith faster and more consistent:

Changed all new Object() references to { }
Changed all for (i=0; i<xxx.length; i++) to (i=0, len=xxx.length; i<len; i++) - some loops are nested so shaves 10s/100s milliseconds on 560 or similarly large LOs, depending on features (pagelinks, glossary, etc) in use...

Please keep out of v2 just now for further testing...

git-svn-id: https://xerteonlinetoolkits.googlecode.com/svn/trunk@1060 912cdd6b-5c7d-d5a7-a2ba-d0f0cdb91641

=======================================================

272398210: Wed Jul 24 09:07:55 2013 +0000 John Smith
OPTIMISATION: Changed a few things to make xenith faster and more consistent:

Changed all new Object() references to { }
Changed all for (i=0; i<xxx.length; i++) to (i=0, len=xxx.length; i<len; i++) - some loops are nested so shaves 10s/100s milliseconds on 560 or similarly large LOs, depending on features (pagelinks, glossary, etc) in use...

Please keep out of v2 just now for further testing...

git-svn-id: https://xerteonlinetoolkits.googlecode.com/svn/trunk@1060 912cdd6b-5c7d-d5a7-a2ba-d0f0cdb91641

=======================================================

24d9bc856: Wed Jul 24 08:56:07 2013 +0000 John Smith
** FIX to remove Ascii Chr(1) from XML during save as it breaks the XML parsing in both xenith and in play.php (where it is parsed to get the LO title). **

Note: other characters that could come from Word or elsewhere (Chr 147, 148, etc ) don't appear to break the XML but perhaps we should still remove or change - perhaps requires a routine in the new editor...

git-svn-id: https://xerteonlinetoolkits.googlecode.com/svn/trunk@1059 912cdd6b-5c7d-d5a7-a2ba-d0f0cdb91641

