8e900abf0: Mon Jul 16 14:54:54 2012 +0000 ronm123
Noticed (and committed) previously that the QR code page had stopped working due to one of the external sites used. This is a 1.8 XOT fix and I have a similar fix for 1.7. That previous revision was since overwritten by a set of revisions committed by Julian so this is the fix re-applied. I also need to contact University of Southampton as the fix is using their site to generate the QR code now. 

